        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Cure the Coronavirus Act</b></p> <p>This bill expands the tropical disease priority review voucher program to include COVID-19 (a respiratory disease caused by a novel coronavirus), thereby providing manufacturers with incentives for development of a vaccine.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
